      "updated": 1783244412215,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Trigger -> single Json meta \nRules -> List of rules\nAction -> will contain list of rules satisfaction as a filterList\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Trigger -> single Json meta \nRules -> List of rules\nAction -> will contain list of rules satisfaction as a filterList\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "W_1gZjjzAkZAw4hGSreQ2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1196.6373796455382,
      "y": 3730.1252446779936,
      "width": 1182.9993896484375,
      "height": 775,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6m",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 362819742,
      "version": 917,
      "versionNonce": 347130780,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783244412215,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "what my json will look like \nWorkflow\n\n    id         int\n    version.   int \n    createdAt. date\n    updatedAt  date      \n    name     string\n    nodes    [Node] ->.      \n                            id\n                            type -> enum (Action/Rule/Wait/Trigger)\n                            condition\n                            operations -> [Operations]  ->\n                                                                    id                   int\n                                                                    attributeName.   string\n                                                                    dataType         BOOLEAN/INTEGER/STRING....\n                                                                    condition          eq/btw/in.... \n                                                                    values              list of dataType value\n                             \n    edges    [Edge] ->  \n                            from    int\n                            to       int\n                            branch  string(true / false/timeout/success.....)\n\n    triggers [Trigger] ->\n                            id \n                            type -> ENTRY || EXIT\n                            event -> x\n                            operations-> [Operations]           // can be empty if dont want to set a attribute level condition\n\n                            ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "what my json will look like \nWorkflow\n\n    id         int\n    version.   int \n    createdAt. date\n    updatedAt  date      \n    name     string\n    nodes    [Node] ->.      \n                            id\n                            type -> enum (Action/Rule/Wait/Trigger)\n                            condition\n                            operations -> [Operations]  ->\n                                                                    id                   int\n                                                                    attributeName.   string\n                                                                    dataType         BOOLEAN/INTEGER/STRING....\n                                                                    condition          eq/btw/in.... \n                                                                    values              list of dataType value\n                             \n    edges    [Edge] ->  \n                            from    int\n                            to       int\n                            branch  string(true / false/timeout/success.....)\n\n    triggers [Trigger] ->\n                            id \n                            type -> ENTRY || EXIT\n                            event -> x\n                            operations-> [Operations]           // can be empty if dont want to set a attribute level condition\n\n                            ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "lLbtL6Ltk1V5rtulmIDT4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1790.9625778173772,
      "y": 4543.315913010395,
      "width": 425.7998046875,
      "height": 925,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6n",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1082105922,
      "version": 453,
      "versionNonce": 1682459684,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783244412215,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Grammer.yml\ngrammar:\n  BOOLEAN:\n    eq:\n      expr: \"{attr} == {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n\n  INTEGER:\n    lt:\n      expr: \"{attr} < {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n    gt:\n      expr: \"{attr} > {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n    eq:\n      expr: \"{attr} == {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n    lte:\n      expr: \"{attr} <= {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n    gte:\n      expr: \"{attr} >= {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n    btw:\n      expr: \"{attr} >= {0} && {attr} <= {1}\"\n      values_expected: 2\n    in:\n      expr: \"{attr} IN {values}\"        \n      values_expected: -1              \n\n  STRING:\n    eq:\n      expr: \"{attr} == {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n    in:\n      expr: \"{attr} IN {values}\"\n      values_expected: -1",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Grammer.yml\ngrammar:\n  BOOLEAN:\n    eq:\n      expr: \"{attr} == {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n\n  INTEGER:\n    lt:\n      expr: \"{attr} < {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n    gt:\n      expr: \"{attr} > {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n    eq:\n      expr: \"{attr} == {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n    lte:\n      expr: \"{attr} <= {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n    gte:\n      expr: \"{attr} >= {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n    btw:\n      expr: \"{attr} >= {0} && {attr} <= {1}\"\n      values_expected: 2\n    in:\n      expr: \"{attr} IN {values}\"        \n      values_expected: -1              \n\n  STRING:\n    eq:\n      expr: \"{attr} == {0}\"\n      values_expected: 1\n    in:\n      expr: \"{attr} IN {values}\"\n      values_expected: -1",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
