      "text": "Workflow Run\n\n\nid                      string                                        unique run identifier\nworkflowId           string                                       which workflow definition\nworkflowVersion     int                                           version it started with (immutable)\norgId                 string                                       whose run (for lookup/filtering)\nstatus                enum                                        RUNNING | WAITING | COMPLETED | FAILED\ncurrentNodeId       int          \ncontextSnapshot   Map<K,V>                                   signal attributes frozen at trigger time\ndelayMeta            object                                       only populated when status=WAITING\n                                  resumeAt       epoch\n                                  waitType       TIME | EVENT\n                                  expectedEvent  string\ntriggerSignalId      string                                        for dedupe\ncreatedAt           timestamp\nupdatedAt          timestamp\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20.60260348937357,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Workflow Run\n\n\nid                      string                                        unique run identifier\nworkflowId           string                                       which workflow definition\nworkflowVersion     int                                           version it started with (immutable)\norgId                 string                                       whose run (for lookup/filtering)\nstatus                enum                                        RUNNING | WAITING | COMPLETED | FAILED\ncurrentNodeId       int          \ncontextSnapshot   Map<K,V>                                   signal attributes frozen at trigger time\ndelayMeta            object                                       only populated when status=WAITING\n                                  resumeAt       epoch\n                                  waitType       TIME | EVENT\n                                  expectedEvent  string\ntriggerSignalId      string                                        for dedupe\ncreatedAt           timestamp\nupdatedAt          timestamp\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
