    {
      "id": "1IuuetGtM5P7eb381YtJL",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1206.0801647422813,
      "y": 10292.787529293519,
      "width": 1003.6394653320312,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b9P",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1704399594,
      "version": 1859,
      "versionNonce": 262953206,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783180371671,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Final decided flow\n1. get the string first if it does not exits if it exits return the code use the same get function then \n    hash the url given plus uuid to a alphamumeric value of length 8\n2. if custom value given map it with the custom value\n3. before creation if bloom filter is giving me that it exits \n    check in db if it exits it exits.. false in bloom or db the url/ hash is returned\n4. if there is conflict and its custom url send the error else retry the complete process \n    again for 3 times else throw some 5xx error..\n    each retry generates a new UUID, not just a new hash of the same input.\n5. add a ttl in a field with the expiry unix timestamp\n6. table index will be on short_code ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Final decided flow\n1. get the string first if it does not exits if it exits return the code use the same get function then \n    hash the url given plus uuid to a alphamumeric value of length 8\n2. if custom value given map it with the custom value\n3. before creation if bloom filter is giving me that it exits \n    check in db if it exits it exits.. false in bloom or db the url/ hash is returned\n4. if there is conflict and its custom url send the error else retry the complete process \n    again for 3 times else throw some 5xx error..\n    each retry generates a new UUID, not just a new hash of the same input.\n5. add a ttl in a field with the expiry unix timestamp\n6. table index will be on short_code ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
