      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783179508071,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1.Ratelimiting will be done on gateway side\n     but as i have to write a single service as stated in the problem so \n     on ratelimit on service as middleware same logic will be implemented on gateway in future..44\n2.adding a middleware in my local service for that\nwill use sliding window of token to flow i will be setting \n80 percent of throughput my infra can handle to be a window limit\n3. will add fixed window ratelimit for a ip so that ddos can be protected \n    from a ip\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1.Ratelimiting will be done on gateway side\n     but as i have to write a single service as stated in the problem so \n     on ratelimit on service as middleware same logic will be implemented on gateway in future..44\n2.adding a middleware in my local service for that\nwill use sliding window of token to flow i will be setting \n80 percent of throughput my infra can handle to be a window limit\n3. will add fixed window ratelimit for a ip so that ddos can be protected \n    from a ip\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
